          <div><svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="1.3" style={{ margin: "0 auto" }}><path d="M5 8h14l-1 12H6L5 8Z" /><path d="M9 8a3 3 0 0 1 6 0" /></svg><p style={{ margin: "14px 0 0", fontSize: 14 }}>Your cart is empty.</p></div>
